# Phoenix ROM files - copyrighted by Amstar (1981)
# These files are required to build the Phoenix FPGA bitstream
# but cannot be distributed due to copyright restrictions.
#
# To obtain these ROMs:
# 1. Download phoenix.zip from a MAME ROM set (e.g., MAME 0.37b+)
# 2. Extract the contents to this directory
#
# Required files:
#   b1-ic39.3b    - Foreground tile ROM (IC39)
#   b2-ic40.4b    - Foreground tile ROM (IC40)
#   ic23.3d       - Background tile ROM (IC23)
#   ic24.4d       - Background tile ROM (IC24)
#   ic45          - Program ROM (IC45)
#   ic46          - Program ROM (IC46)
#   ic47          - Program ROM (IC47)
#   ic48          - Program ROM (IC48)
#   h5-ic49.5a    - Program ROM (IC49)
#   h6-ic50.6a    - Program ROM (IC50)
#   h7-ic51.7a    - Program ROM (IC51)
#   h8-ic52.8a    - Program ROM (IC52)
#   mmi6301.ic40  - Palette PROM (IC40)
#   mmi6301.ic41  - Palette PROM (IC41)
#
# MAME CRC checksums (for verification):
#   b1-ic39.3b:   CRC 53413e8f  SHA1 d772358505b973b10da840d204afb210c0c746ec
